      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "textContent": "<br><b>Hiking trail of about 3 hours and 10km long.</b><br> From Casa Petri yard you will notice the view to the 'Cârnic' massif - a mountain that has been massively exploited even since antiquity to extract gold. From the historic center go to the 'Cetate' open pit and then to the Cârnic galleries. Along a pine forest hike to the protected area 'Piatra Corbului' and Sphinx. The next destination is Lety and Șulei massif and on your way to the historic center will pass by Tăul Mare (lake) and Văidoaia Gallery."
        }
      ]
